day, which is the sun.

67
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:06,262
And God has created that, like, as a lamp.

68
00:05:06,631 --> 00:05:14,469
And the moon at night, especially when it's full, like last night or whatever, and you cannot miss it, the beauty of it, the light of it.

69
00:05:14,469 --> 00:05:17,308
It just brightens everything.

70
00:05:17,308 --> 00:05:23,682
You, I woke up in the middle of the night, last night. I just saw it and it was just through the curtain, my (unintelligible) was just real bright.

71
00:05:24,729 --> 00:05:30,375
So here, these creations are placed and, you know, around
us.

72
00:05:30,375 --> 00:05:36,909
And how blind these people are not to notice that and not to realize it, not to even think about it.

73
00:05:37,353 --> 00:05:42,204
